{{Quote|Just fake it ... I'm so good no one will notice you can't play ... Just a few 'whee-whoas' on the choruses ... No solos or anything ... Wastewater is my life, but music is a close second.|Swanny Mull, to Jedi Obi-Wan Kenobi and Anakin Skywalker|<ref name="Jedi Quest: The Shadow Trap">''[[Jedi Quest: The Shadow Trap]]''</ref>}}
'''Swanny and the Rooters''' were a band founded by [[Swanny Mull]] shortly after the [[Battle of Naboo/Legends|Battle of Naboo]] that frequently performed at [[Decca Besadii Diori|Decca]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt's]] base. Swanny at one point helped [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] and [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] gain entrance to Decca's lair, using them in the band in return. The Rooters were nearly destroyed when a group of [[Granta Omega|Striker's]] men attacked Decca's compound.

==Appearances==
